ons and infinite resummation therein. Our interpretation also\nindicate that holographic dual of these gauge theories is provided by certain\nnon-critical string theories.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Dec 2009 21:02:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 5 Jan 2010 00:20:21 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 9 Dec 2010 11:39:58 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 1 Feb 2011 12:03:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-02-02"}
