ple. Accounting for measurement precision, we place an upper limit on the\nradial-velocity dispersion of the cluster of 0.81 +/- 0.08 km/s. After\ncorrecting for undetected binaries, we derive a true radial-velocity dispersion\nof 0.65 +/- 0.10 km/s.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Dec 2009 21:47:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-14"}
